Contributor Guidelines

Thank you for contributing to gheese.

Before submitting changes:

- make sure your changes are relevant to the project
- keep documentation up to date when behavior changes
- run the project's existing checks before opening a pull request
- sign off your commits to comply with the Developer Certificate of Origin

Use:

```bash
git commit -s
```

By contributing to this repository, you agree to the terms in the [`DCO`](./DCO).
